On Saturday there will be a protest public assembly, on Monday - on the day of the final vote on the Health Insurance Act - work will be stopped.
The event will certainly cause serious disruption of transport, as railway transport will almost completely stop and the staff of the Budapest Transport Company (BKV) will be on strike within 13 hours.
